query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('arithmetic-geometry',
'color',
'contour-integration',
'email',
'factorial',
'gauge-theory',
'header-footer',
'line-breaking',
'listings',
'mass',
'rotational-dynamics',
'self-learning',
'uniform-convergence',
'vector-bundles',
'xetex')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math',
'mathoverflow',
'physics',
'serverfault',
'tex') group by t1.name;
